title: Quictent Galvanized Raised Garden Bed 6x3x2 Ft with 3 pcs Tomato Cage 1 pc Weed Barrier Gloves, Bottomless Metal Planter Box Vegetabes Flowers Herbs Backyard Patio
feature_bullets: [" 【Extra-Height】Metal raised garden bed is 22.4\" height, normal height is only 12\". You can add mutiple material at the bottom layer to creat nutrient-rich soil; grow many deep roots vegetables or fruits; also tall garden bed can keep out small pets like chiken, puppies, rabbits."," 【Tomato Cage Included】We provide customer with 3 pcs tomato supporting cage, and a weed barrier for galvanized garden bed to keep weeds out of planting zone. Tomato cage can support plants, prevent plants from falling down because of their own or fruits'weight."," 【Bottomless Design】Open bottom of metal planter bed is good for drainage, plant roots won't be sick from eccessive water. Also plants' roots won't touch the metal sheet, can obsorb variant nutrition from soil, and grow more healthily."," 【Built To Last】Garden raised planting bed is made of galvanized steel panel, assure fine condition of metal garden bed, it's able to stand harsh weather conditions, won't crack in years, use without worry."," 【Strengthen Stabilizing Bars】The reinforced middle crossbar for 6 ft long raised garden box is cylindrical, won't bend easily like aluminium flat bar. Our supporting bar can keep metal garden planter more stable, and refuse crack at joints on the middle of long metal sheets."]
